---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Conor McArdle \u2014 Digital Communications, Video, Design"
description: "Portfolio of Conor McArdle, Digital Communications Specialist at the MIT School of Engineering. Video, photography, web design, and institutional storytelling."
navKey: home
statusPath: "~/portfolio/index.html"
permalink: /
---

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero__content">
      <p class="hero__label">// welcome</p>
      <h1 class="hero__name">Conor McArdle</h1>
      <p class="hero__role">Digital Communications Specialist at MIT</p>
      <p class="hero__tagline">
        <span data-typed="I help institutions tell their story — through strategy, design, video, photography, and the web."></span><span class="cursor">|</span>
      </p>
      <nav class="hero-quicklinks" aria-label="Quick links">
        <a href="#about" class="about-quicklink">About Me</a>
        <a href="#work" class="about-quicklink">Featured Work</a>
        <a href="/work/" class="about-quicklink">All Work</a>
        <a href="/contact/" class="about-quicklink">Contact</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Introduction -->
<section id="about" class="section section--intro" data-animate>
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section__label">// about me</p>
    <div class="intro-row">
      <div class="headshot">
        <img src="/images/bio/headshot.jpeg" alt="Conor McArdle" loading="lazy">
      </div>
      <p class="intro">I am a communications professional with experience spanning education and higher ed — from independent school classrooms to the Massachusetts Institute of Technology. I shoot, edit, design, write, build websites, manage social media, and lead projects. What ties it all together is a belief that institutions do their best work when they communicate honestly, with craft and care, about the things that matter most.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Featured Work -->
<section id="work" class="section section--alt">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section__label" data-animate>// featured work</p>
    <div class="cards-grid cards-grid--home">
      {% for item in collections.featuredWork %}
      <article class="card" data-animate data-animate-delay="{{ loop.index }}">
        <a href="{{ item.url }}" class="card__link">
          <div class="card__image">
            {% if item.data.cardImage %}
            <img src="{{ item.data.cardImage }}" alt="{{ item.data.cardImageAlt }}" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:top;">
            {% else %}
            <div class="card__image-placeholder">{{ item.data.cardPlaceholder }}</div>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
          <div class="card__body">
            <span class="card__number">{{ item.data.featuredOrder | padStart(2) }}</span>
            <h3 class="card__title">{{ item.data.cardTitle }}</h3>
            <p class="card__desc">{{ item.data.cardDesc }}</p>
            <div class="card__meta">
              <span class="card__meta-item"><span class="card__meta-key">role:</span> {{ item.data.cardRole }}</span>
              <span class="card__meta-item"><span class="card__meta-key">year:</span> {{ item.data.cardTimeline }}</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
